to the Olympic Games through 2032, which are scheduled for Paris (2024), Milan Cortina (2026), Los Angeles (2028) and Brisbane (2032).\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999996671527341, \"rank\": 3.3268213458549225e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3573, \"end\": 3578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3979478512282517e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The host city for the 2030 Olympic Winter Games has not yet been chosen.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT NBCUNIVERSAL  NBCUniversal is one of the world's leading media and entertainment companies in the development, production, and marketing of entertainment, news, sports and information to a global audience.\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3729, \"end\": 3741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999996671527341, \"rank\": 3.3268213458549225e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUNIVERSAL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3743, \"end\": 3755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999996671527341, \"rank\": 3.3268213458549225e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal owns and operates a valuable portfolio of news and entertainment television networks, a premier motion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 4224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3935, \"end\": 3947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999996671527341, \"rank\": 3.3268213458549225e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4225, \"end\": 4237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999996671527341, \"rank\": 3.3268213458549225e-07, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 4257, \"end\": 4276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Comcast Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT IMAX CORPORATION  IMAX, an innovator in entertainment technology, combines proprietary software, architecture, and equipment to create experiences that take you beyond the edge of your seat to a world you have never imagined.\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Top filmmakers and studios are utilizing IMAX systems to connect with audiences in extraordinary ways, making IMAX's network among the most important and successful theatrical distribution platforms for major event films around the globe.\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4621, \"end\": 4625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\", \"score\": 0.9999792329609558, \"rank\": 2.0767470530817315e-05, \"text\": \"IMAX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4751, \"end\": 4761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999998576641, \"rank\": 1.4234220532046318e-10, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 4910, \"to\": 4955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5104, \"entities\": []}]}"